reviewText: A bit long, but IF you are LDS, it won't matter!  Good production, and accurate!
Laughable, about a "Prophet" who created a religion and now plenty of people believe in it.
Great product and such a great reasonable price.  I am very pleased!
I watch it and all is well and if you are wondering if it is true, it is. Thanks for the fast mailing.

True but sad reading...Joseph Smith was a true Prophet Of God & crucified for it..On judgement day I would not want to be those who killed him..Lucky for them they can repent & be forgiven as we have a loving God..I am very happy I bought this book for my library..
